summary: So I’m not sure what I’m most excited about for season 8 but the moment Jon and Daenerys find out about Jon’s parentage has got...
body:
So I’m not sure what I’m most excited about for season 8 but the moment Jon and Daenerys find out about Jon’s parentage has got to be very near the top of the list because their reactions are going to be the exact opposite of the other person’s.

Jon is going to throw up when he finds out he shagged his aunt and give some kind of “I-didn’t-ask-for-this”-speech about the whole oops, I’m the heir to the Iron Throne thing.

Daenerys probably won’t mind the accidental incest, but imagine the fit she will throw when she finds out that Jon “too little for me” Snow has a better claim to the throne than she does.

And Arya and Sansa are going to be there like, bring out the popcorn

RULES: Number your top ten favorite characters from different fandoms. Then tag ten people!

I was tagged by @ktwrites
